IMAGING DATA ORIGINAL TIFF FILES
We have uploaded all the original imaging files to Zenodo: https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.11619572. 
Information on the hairpins and probe sets used for HCR in situ hybridizations has also been added to the Zenodo repository alongside the imaging data.



